title: Kurt Seligmann Exotic Garden Tote
description:
Tote developed from Kurt Seligmann’s Exotic garden, 1954, from the Art Institute of Chicago’s collection.

The ethereal botanicals of Kurt Seligmann's (American, born Switzerland, 1900-1962) grace our tote.  Warm colors and enchanting imagery provide shelter, convenience and style; a true benefit of a dreary day.  

  • Dimensions: 16 1/2 x 12 x 5 in.
  • Materials: Polyester, microfiber lining.
  • Interior pocket with zip closure.
